No.

53
00:03:59,292 --> 00:04:00,417
"BOOS"
How stingy.

54
00:04:00,417 --> 00:04:03,167
Duh! Life isn't that simple.

55
00:04:03,167 --> 00:04:05,083
By the way, are you a robber?

56
