83
00:05:25,083 --> 00:05:26,750
Be confident, Mr. Alvin.

84
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:28,833
It's funny anyway.

85
00:05:28,833 --> 00:05:30,708
What do you mean?

86
00:05:30,708 --> 00:05:32,250
I don't want to perform.

87
00:05:35,833 --> 00:05:39,625
No. Why are you sitting down?
I said I'm not going to perform.

88
00:05:42,292 --> 00:05:46,208
Stop it.
Don't be like you're going to watch a show!

89
00:05:51,958 --> 00:05:55,958
Alvin. Alvin.

90
00:05:55,958 --> 00:05:59,250
-Don't push me.
-Alvin. Alvin.

91
00:05:59,250 --> 00:06:06,333
Alvin, Alvin...

92
00:06:06,333 --> 00:06:07,750
Homeless dog.

93
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:11,333
Geez, close your eyes and wait.

94
00:06:11,333 --> 00:06:13,000
Don't open before I tell you to.

95
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:15,417
And it has nothing to do with a homeless dog.

96
00:06:15,417 --> 00:06:16,958
He's going to perform.

97
00:06:17,792 --> 00:06:20,875
My talent…

98
00:06:25,375 --> 00:06:27,250
Okay, I'm ready.

99
00:06:28,042 --> 00:06:29,458
Check this out.

100
