102
00:06:52,958 --> 00:06:54,208
Okay.

103
00:06:54,208 --> 00:06:55,958
Wait a minute.

104
00:07:00,625 --> 00:07:02,458
Here you go.

105
00:07:02,458 --> 00:07:03,708
Do you really want to give it to me?

106
00:07:03,708 --> 00:07:06,000
As an apology for showing you boring talent.

107
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,958
Thank you. Goodbye.

108
00:07:08,958 --> 00:07:10,625
Be safe.

109
00:07:13,417 --> 00:07:14,917
You're great indeed, Mr. Alvin.

110
00:07:14,917 --> 00:07:19,625
Making others lose the will to fight.
That's your way of fighting, right?

111
00:07:20,917 --> 00:07:22,375
Yes...

112
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:43,167
Geez.

113
00:07:46,375 --> 00:07:49,542
No way. The golem is too strong.

114
00:07:49,542 --> 00:07:50,583
Mr. Alvin.

115
00:07:50,583 --> 00:07:52,125
Carla, step back.

116
00:07:54,292 --> 00:07:56,000
I'll buy you some time. Run away...

117
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:59,792
Impossible. You can't buy us any time.

118
00:07:59,792 --> 00:08:01,125
Absolutely no way.

119
00:08:01,125 --> 00:08:02,583
You deny it too much.

120
00:08:02,583 --> 00:08:04,167
Not even if you were reborn.

121
00:08:04,167 --> 00:08:05,667
How annoying you are.

122
00:08:05,667 --> 00:08:08,208
Hey, you. I'm as a forward...

123
00:08:10,125 --> 00:08:12,250
We're talking. Shut up!

124
00:08:16,958 --> 00:08:18,917
All right.

125
00:08:18,917 --> 00:08:22,833
Do you think you can fight with the golem
for more than ten seconds?

126
00:08:22,833 --> 00:08:26,333
You can't, right?
Since you're not capable of doing it.

127
00:08:26,333 --> 00:08:29,625
The answer hurts a lot, yet it's right.

128
00:08:29,625 --> 00:08:32,250
However,

129
00:08:32,250 --> 00:08:35,625
you have one thing that others don't.

130
00:08:37,375 --> 00:08:38,417
Is it virtue?

131
00:08:38,417 --> 00:08:39,750
How hilarious.

132
00:08:41,167 --> 00:08:43,708
It's me. Yeah.

133
00:08:43,708 --> 00:08:45,042
I want to lose it.

134
00:08:45,042 --> 00:08:47,958
I'll assist you as a healer.

135
00:08:47,958 --> 00:08:50,333
Beating a golem is a piece of cheese.

136
00:08:50,333 --> 00:08:52,375
It should be a piece of cake.

137
00:08:52,375 --> 00:08:54,000
Assist me?

138
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:57,333
Are you going to use killing magic?

139
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,583
It'll be all right this time.

140
00:09:01,583 --> 00:09:04,333
I've grown after that.

141
00:09:06,125 --> 00:09:07,667
Really?

142
00:09:07,667 --> 00:09:10,917
Unlike someone who has stopped growing.

143
00:09:10,917 --> 00:09:13,042
Don't point at others.

144
00:09:13,042 --> 00:09:16,000
All right. The golem is waiting for you.

145
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,125
I'll assist you well.

146
00:09:18,125 --> 00:09:20,083
Will it really be all right?

147
00:09:20,083 --> 00:09:21,542
I'll pick up your bones.

148
00:09:21,542 --> 00:09:23,458
That's unlucky.

149
00:09:25,458 --> 00:09:26,875
There's no way.

150
00:09:26,875 --> 00:09:28,917
I wish you success in battle.

151
00:09:28,917 --> 00:09:30,500
Golem.

152
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:33,208
I'm a man.

153
00:09:33,208 --> 00:09:35,292
-I won't back down.
-Come on!

154
00:09:35,292 --> 00:09:37,500
-Let's fight...
-Go for it, Mr. Alvin.

155
00:09:37,500 --> 00:09:39,167
"ALVIN"
Go, go, Alvin.

156
00:09:39,167 --> 00:09:40,792
"COME ON"
Come on, come on, Alvin.

157
00:09:40,792 --> 00:09:42,667
"GO"
Let's go, Alvin.

158
00:09:42,667 --> 00:09:46,583
Challenge a battle that you can't win
and recognize your strength.

159
00:09:46,583 --> 00:09:48,125
Shut up!

160
00:09:48,958 --> 00:09:52,375
How's the new magic, "yellow cheers"?

161
00:09:52,375 --> 00:09:54,042
You're just adding trouble.

162
00:09:54,042 --> 00:09:55,958
Your power is overwhelming, right?

163
00:09:55,958 --> 00:09:58,208
My anger is overwhelming.

164
00:09:58,208 --> 00:09:59,750
There should be other assistance magic.

165
00:09:59,750 --> 00:10:01,542
Like increasing attack.

166
00:10:01,542 --> 00:10:05,042
Strengthening defense.
The magic that's useful to the fight.

167
00:10:05,042 --> 00:10:06,250
I see.

168
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:09,250
I'll buy an expensive sword
and shield from the town then.

169
00:10:09,250 --> 00:10:10,292
I'll be right back.

170
00:10:10,292 --> 00:10:13,833
No, no, no. It's not like that.

171
00:10:13,833 --> 00:10:16,208
I did such a silly thing.

172
00:10:16,208 --> 00:10:19,708
You haven't given me money, oops.

173
00:10:19,708 --> 00:10:21,000
That's not what I meant.

174
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:23,750
Since you're a healer,
you should use magic to assist me.

175
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:25,833
About this...

176
00:10:25,833 --> 00:10:30,000
I think you can't beat the golem
even if I make you stronger.

177
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,583
You hit a nerve in me.

178
00:10:32,583 --> 00:10:37,875
Didn't you say it's a piece of cake?
But you can do nothing.

179
00:10:39,708 --> 00:10:41,333
I still have a secret skill.

180
00:10:41,333 --> 00:10:42,417
What's that?

181
00:10:42,417 --> 00:10:45,083
You'll win with this, but...

182
00:10:48,792 --> 00:10:50,708
I don't know why you're hesitating.

183
00:10:50,708 --> 00:10:52,750
Since we get here, I'd sacrifice myself.

184
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:56,042
Let's work together to beat the golem.

185
00:10:56,792 --> 00:10:58,625
Mr. Alvin.

186
00:10:58,625 --> 00:11:00,292
I got it.

187
00:11:00,958 --> 00:11:02,083
What?

188
00:11:02,083 --> 00:11:05,042
I'll borrow the power of the earth spirits.

189
00:11:06,125 --> 00:11:08,042
That sounds great.

190
00:11:10,042 --> 00:11:13,542
It needs strong praying power for the spirits.

191
00:11:13,542 --> 00:11:16,750
So let's pray together, Mr. Alvin.

192
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:19,375
Got it. We just have to pray, right?

193
00:11:19,375 --> 00:11:21,417
Kneel and put your hands on the ground.

194
00:11:21,417 --> 00:11:23,292
Keep your head down.

195
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:28,708
Sorry to keep you waiting.

196
00:11:28,708 --> 00:11:30,208
Well...

197
00:11:30,208 --> 00:11:34,125
I have something to tell you before the fight.

198
00:11:34,125 --> 00:11:37,875
This warrior hopes you let him win.

199
00:11:37,875 --> 00:11:39,333
Please.

200
00:11:39,333 --> 00:11:41,750
How dare you trick me.

201
00:11:50,958 --> 00:11:53,250
We almost reach the town.

202
00:11:53,250 --> 00:11:56,333
It seems someone is missing.

203
00:11:56,333 --> 00:11:58,708
Maybe he's chasing butterflies again.

204
00:12:02,625 --> 00:12:04,875
It's that golem.

205
00:12:10,708 --> 00:12:14,042
What? He's trying to tell us something.

206
00:12:14,042 --> 00:12:16,875
What did you say?

207
00:12:16,875 --> 00:12:19,167
Why do you understand?

208
00:12:19,167 --> 00:12:21,625
So what did he say?

209
00:12:23,375 --> 00:12:25,667
Just say it if you don't understand.

210
00:12:25,667 --> 00:12:29,292
That's why I asked "what did you say?".

211
00:12:29,292 --> 00:12:32,333
That's like you understood it. Fool.

212
00:12:32,333 --> 00:12:34,708
Both of you, listen to me!

213
00:12:34,708 --> 00:12:37,125
So you can talk?

214
00:12:37,708 --> 00:12:39,917
I heard that monsters

215
00:12:39,917 --> 00:12:43,500
would be highly intelligent and experienced
after living for a long time.

216
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:45,542
Don't explain it anymore.

217
00:12:45,542 --> 00:12:49,708
Just follow me. It's urgent.

218
00:13:03,875 --> 00:13:06,917
What's wrong with him?

219
00:13:06,917 --> 00:13:09,375
He's poisoned.

220
00:13:09,375 --> 00:13:11,792
I think a poisonous snake bit him.

221
00:13:11,792 --> 00:13:15,917
Mushroom monsters should
have the ability to resist poison.

222
00:13:15,917 --> 00:13:23,333
I'm an... edible... mushroom...

223
00:13:23,333 --> 00:13:25,208
Oh, right...

224
00:13:25,208 --> 00:13:29,250
Are you okay? Do you have anything to say?

225
00:13:29,250 --> 00:13:31,833
Detoxification way...

226
00:13:31,833 --> 00:13:35,250
Don't talk.
The poison will circulate all over the body.

227
00:13:35,250 --> 00:13:38,708
Please don't say it's the last goodbye.

228
00:13:38,708 --> 00:13:40,542
He didn't say that.

229
00:13:40,542 --> 00:13:49,167
Sobbing, I wish, sobbing, in the next life,
sobbing, we'll meet again, sobbing.

230
00:13:49,167 --> 00:13:50,917
Don't give up curing him.

231
00:13:50,917 --> 00:13:53,958
It's the first time I've seen someone sobbing.

232
00:13:53,958 --> 00:13:57,958
Others usually give up at this time.

233
00:13:57,958 --> 00:14:01,000
Luckily I'm here.

234
00:14:02,292 --> 00:14:05,833
Look at his look of despair.

235
00:14:05,833 --> 00:14:07,458
Let me show you

236
00:14:07,458 --> 00:14:10,042
holy power in the super healing list.

237
00:14:10,042 --> 00:14:12,375
Are you sure it's not a blacklist?

238
00:14:12,375 --> 00:14:15,417
Have you forgotten that
I rejuvenated the old lady young?

239
00:14:15,417 --> 00:14:18,583
But I also remember your killing magic.

240
00:14:18,583 --> 00:14:20,833
Are you ready?

241
00:14:20,833 --> 00:14:22,750
Whatever.

242
00:14:23,667 --> 00:14:25,958
He's ready for death.

243
00:14:27,292 --> 00:14:30,167
Come and lean against this rock.

244
00:14:31,708 --> 00:14:33,958
Right. Take it slow.

245
00:14:35,125 --> 00:14:37,208
It looks like...

246
00:14:37,208 --> 00:14:40,292
It's okay. Calm down.

247
00:14:40,292 --> 00:14:41,750
I'm sorry...

248
00:14:42,542 --> 00:14:44,917
She kind of does look like a healer...

249
00:14:44,917 --> 00:14:48,083
I'll put you to sleep right away.

250
00:14:48,083 --> 00:14:51,542
No way. Her choice of words is like a devil.

251
00:14:51,542 --> 00:14:54,375
With my holy left hand.

252
00:15:10,625 --> 00:15:12,208
What are you doing?

253
00:15:12,208 --> 00:15:14,792
What are you doing with your hand in his mouth?

254
00:15:14,792 --> 00:15:15,917
Stop it!

255
00:15:15,917 --> 00:15:18,167
No, it's detoxification magic.

256
00:15:18,167 --> 00:15:19,625
You're torturing him.

257
00:15:19,625 --> 00:15:22,625
It's okay. I just let him spit out the poison.

258
00:15:22,625 --> 00:15:24,542
Don't dig out his guts.

259
00:15:28,042 --> 00:15:31,833
It works. You spit the poison out.

260
00:15:32,958 --> 00:15:35,458
How is it? How do you feel?

261
00:15:35,458 --> 00:15:39,250
I feel... much better...

262
00:15:39,250 --> 00:15:42,667
You're a healer indeed.
I thought I was going to die.

263
00:15:42,667 --> 00:15:45,708
Don't be like that.

264
00:15:45,708 --> 00:15:48,417
I'm tired of being praised

